    "headline": "Investors Game Out Stagflation Risk in Japan as Oil Prices Rise",
    "summary": "(Bloomberg) -- Some investors are starting to position for a scenario Japan hasn’t faced in decades, as rising oil prices and a weaker currency stoke stagflation worries and force a rethink of bets.Global funds including Allianz Global Investors and Amundi SA are already hedging against stagflation — a mix of rising prices and slowing growth — with the Iran conflict nearing the one-month mark. Allianz has reinforced its underweight view on Japanese government bonds and turned neutral on equities",
